## v0.0.1

* Initial release

## v0.0.2

* added some options and logging

## v0.0.1alpha

* Heh, but it is still in dev. So let's call it alpha

## v0.0.4

* Fixed stackoverflow on retrying request after failing
* added `req.retry` method to retry http request in error handlers

## v0.0.5

* Added some minor fixes

## v0.0.6

* Added skip functionality
* Added some docs
* Added "response_body" and "response_header" shortcuts

## v0.0.7

* Rescuing of Retry Exception is removed to Base class, so it will be triggered in context of main loop (it will executed with global sleep timeout)
* Added `headers` callback support

## v0.0.8

* em-http-request options support added

## v0.0.9

* pushing request_opt to init